[SN]TITLE[SN]
Vodafone creates 100 customer services jobs in Cardiff

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Vodafone is to create 100 customer service jobs in Cardiff as part of more than 2,100 new roles across the UK.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The phone company said the new Cardiff roles, at its third-party customer service centre in the city, would enhance its quality of service.
The jobs are part of a Â£2bn investment programme in Vodafone's UK network and services.
They come as part of expansions at contact centres in Manchester, Newcastle, Stoke and Glasgow.
